## Phase 3: KPI Development

| Metric             | Description                            |
| ------------------ | -------------------------------------- |
| Total Orders       | Count of total transactions            |
| Total Revenue      | SUM(Price_INR) â€” shown in INR Millions |
| Average Dish Price | AVG(Price_INR)                         |
| Average Rating     | AVG(Rating)                            |


## Deep-Dive Analytical KPIs

| Category       | Insights                                                                 |
| -------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Date-Based     | Monthly / Quarterly trends, Year-over-year growth, Weekday order pattern |
| Location-Based | Top 10 cities by orders, Revenue contribution by states                  |
| Restaurant     | Top restaurants by orders, price & rating insights                       |
| Cuisine        | Category performance vs rating                                           |
| Dish           | Most ordered dishes & performance ranking                                |
